{"tid":2255031,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"五旬婦原被控去年九月元朗傷人 今被加控暴動及妨礙司法公正","createTime":"2020-10-23T08:44:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-18T14:24:14.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"008db1255c8e8283adc629f112c1f493954576d6","tid":2255031,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T08:44:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/10629\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F10629&d=Z0jJ2Ci5UPqU8nDHOGo4vGlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=171958e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/10629</a><br />\n<br />\n#東區裁判法院第一庭<br />\n#錢禮主任裁判官 #提堂<br />\n👤李(50) #0921元朗<br />\n<br />\n修訂控罪：<br />\n1）有意圖而傷人<br />\n於2019年9月22日在元朗青山公路元朗段162至164號地下的中國銀行外，意圖使男子姚興強身體受嚴重傷害而非法及惡意傷害他<br />\n<br />\n新增控罪：<br />\n2）有意圖而傷人<br />\n 於同日同地意圖使男子X身體受嚴重傷害而非法及惡意傷害他<br />\n<br />\n3）暴動<br />\n於同日同地與其他身份不詳人士參與暴動<br />\n<br />\n4）作出傾向並意圖妨礙司法公正行為<br />\n於2020年6月24日在葵涌一單位將一對鞋抛出窗外，企圖毀滅證據<br />\n<br />\n案件押後至2020年 11月30日 14:30於東區裁判法院第一庭再提堂，待控方準備轉介文件將案件轉介至區域法院。<br />\n<br />\n✅裁判官批准被告以原有條件保釋"},{"pid":"5024f665c350dd9e2a05273fa1939786f55f2181","tid":2255031,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T08:44:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bab19cd72339bc28621e336e353f321d49d71625","tid":2255031,"uid":77196,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T08:47:11.000Z","msg":"咁個的屎佬都應該加控埋暴動啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"259786c2a0375f3ec8c3760ab0a87d8f0c7b5b6e","tid":2255031,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T08:48:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b9e0ef93d7b80cbd74b7c59487c4d7b7f0a269e","tid":2255031,"uid":8014,"like":0,"d